63
00:05:16,850 --> 00:05:21,760
How does nature construct a living thing from
simple chemical components?

64
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:27,030
For example, how does a human emerge nine
months after the unique mixing of its parents’

65
00:05:27,030 --> 00:05:30,640
