egg?

66
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:35,870
When I was a child, these questions were only
just beginning to be answered.

67
00:05:35,870 --> 00:05:41,880
Indeed, just five months before my own birth,
the Nobel committee announced that the 1962

68
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:47,780
prize for physiology or medicine would be
awarded to James Watson, Francis Crick, and

69
00:05:47,780 --> 00:05:57,030
