97
00:08:10,330 --> 00:08:16,050
The thematic link between the above works
is that of structure – atomic structure

98
00:08:16,050 --> 00:08:23,740
– and its implicitly inherent importance
in determining biomolecular activity.

99
00:08:23,740 --> 00:08:29,620
X-rays and, in recent years synchrotron radiation,
have played a central role in this enterprise.

100
00:08:29,620 --> 00:08:35,940
The relevance of these studies goes well beyond
that of pure academic understanding – the

101
00:08:35,940 --> 00:08:40,849
