process, as well as a knowledge of the biochemical

102
00:08:40,849 --> 00:08:47,189
function of the ribosome, are already having
a huge impact on the design of novel antibiotic

103
00:08:47,189 --> 00:08:53,420
substances and other drugs, plus a deeper
understanding of how some cancers arise and

104
00:08:53,420 --> 00:08:55,500
how they might be tackled.

105
00:08:55,500 --> 00:09:02,220
The year that Yonath, Ramakrishnan, and Steitz
were awarded their Nobel prize (2009) also

106
00:09:02,220 --> 00:09:10,080
saw first light at the first hard x-ray free-electron
laser, the Linear Coherent Light Source (or

107
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:13,259
LCLS) at the SLAC facility in Stanford, California.

108
00:09:13,259 --> 00:09:17,649
The first report of an entirely new biological
structure, cathepsin B, determined using the

109
00:09:17,649 --> 00:09:24,560
LCLS was reported a little over three years
later.

110
00:09:24,560 --> 00:09:31,290
XFELs provide x-ray beams with unique properties
regarding pulse duration, peak pulse intensity,

111
00:09:31,290 --> 00:09:33,120
and beam cross-section.

112
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:39,259
Using a technique coined “diffraction-before-destruction”,
crystals with sizes orders of magnitude smaller

113
00:09:39,259 --> 00:09:44,129
