science continues to develop unabated over

116
00:09:54,709 --> 00:09:58,440
100 years since its inception.

117
00:09:58,440 --> 00:10:03,410
Almost immediately since their discovery at
the end of the 19th century, x-rays have played

118
00:10:03,410 --> 00:10:06,790
