source of x-rays.

123
00:10:26,100 --> 00:10:31,459
Modern radiograms expose the patient for durations
typically well under a second and can distinguish

124
00:10:31,459 --> 00:10:34,809
features well under a millimeter in size.

125
00:10:34,809 --> 00:10:41,079
Radiography is today one of the primary diagnostic
tools available to medicine and dentistry.

126
00:10:41,079 --> 00:10:45,939
Other common uses of x-rays are in security,
